				<h1 id="article-title" class="article-title">Sierra Leone: Imminent execution / death penalty / legal concern</h1>
			</header>

			<article class="article-content " aria-labelledby="article-title">
			
				<p>Brigadier Hassan Karim Conteh, Corporal Tamba Gborie, Colonel Samuel Francis Koroma, Major Kula Samba (f), Colonel Abdul Karim Sesay and 29 other soldiers: AI fears that the execution of 34 soldiers could be imminent, after they were sentenced to death by firing squad at a court martial in Freetown on 12 October 1998.</p>
<div class="wp-block-file"><object class="wp-block-file__embed" data="https://www.amnesty.org/en/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/afr510191998en.pdf" type="application/pdf" style="width:100%;height:880px" aria-label="Embed of Sierra Leone: Imminent execution / death penalty / legal concern"></object></div><h3>Choose a language to view report</h3><div class="download-block is-multiple"><div class="checkboxGroup is-control "><button class="checkboxGroup-button" type="button" aria-haspopup="listbox" aria-expanded="false">English	</button><fieldset class="checkboxGroup-list"><span class="checkboxGroup-item"><input id="aa5de18fed50557c5523131c65cd1ee28" class="screen-reader-text" type="radio" name="f7bdc2ae" value="https://www.amnesty.org/en/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/afr510191998en.pdf"><label for="aa5de18fed50557c5523131c65cd1ee28" data-value="https://www.amnesty.org/en/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/afr510191998en.pdf">English</label></span><span class="checkboxGroup-item"><input id="b054229b85471d9c3173faebf14b5cf24" class="screen-reader-text" type="radio" name="f7bdc2ae" value="https://www.amnesty.org/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2021/06/afr510191998es.pdf"><label for="b054229b85471d9c3173faebf14b5cf24" data-value="https://www.amnesty.org/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2021/06/afr510191998es.pdf">Spanish</label></span></fieldset></div><a class="btn btn--download btn--primary" role="button" href="https://www.amnesty.org/en/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/afr510191998en.pdf" download="afr510191998en.pdf">Download PDF</a></div>			</article>

